# Welcome to Devernote!
Devernote is a markdown-based note-taking application created specifically for developers.

I have had a love/hate relationship with Evernote since I started using it and this is response toa lot of the frustrations I have with it.

## Evernote

**Pros:**

- Available anywhere
- Connects with a lot of other websites and services
- Looks nice

**Cons:**

- Formatting often breaks
- Formatting text is a chore
- No syntax highlighting for code blocks

## Devernote

Because Devernote uses markdown, it is incredibly quick to type clean, well-formatted notes without breaking away too much from what you are doing or learning.

It is easy to create a [link](http://www.google.com) or embed images:

