## How was it made?

It was created primarily using Node.js, Express and MongoDB as well as many other additional Node modules, notably Showdown for the markdown to html conversion and Highlight.js for the syntax highlighting.

For further information and to take a look at the app, check out the [project on GitHub](https://github.com/polygami/devernote) or email me at [liam@polygami.co.uk](mailto:liam@polygami.co.uk).
			
